Enum Class RegexPattern.PosixCharClass

java.lang.Object

public static enum RegexPattern.PosixCharClass extends Enum<RegexPattern.PosixCharClass> implements RegexPattern.CharacterProperty
Represents a POSIX character class inside a CharacterSet: e.g. \p{Lower}
